kotline complier version ko change karna se dependencies update karna zaruri nahi hai.
Dependencies ko 3 categories mein divide kiya ja sakta hai:

Kotlin-Dependent Dependencies: Ye directly Kotlin version par depend karti hain
KSP (Kotlin Symbol Processing)
Kotlin Coroutines
Kotlin Serialization
Kotlin Reflect

Android Gradle Plugin (AGP) Compatibility: AGP version ko Kotlin version ke sath compatible hona chahiye
AGP 8.7.3 latest Kotlin versions ke sath compatible hai

Other Dependencies: Android libraries (CoreKtx, Appcompat, etc.) Kotlin version se directly affected nahi hoti
